{"tid":576472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讓吵鬧中國人閉嘴　這招「好賤，不過我喜歡」","createTime":"2018-03-01T02:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T03:08:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20b08a292fa4ea0e2b6fa034f4425927beb69a8e","tid":576472,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"中共近日建議中國修憲，取消「國家主席」的任期限制，被解讀為現任國家主席習近平有意「稱帝」，不但習近平被取新綽號「袁二」（袁：袁世凱，二：二世／次等），連中國人在外都覺得顏面無光。<br />\n一位網友在《PTT》「八卦版」上分享說，他昨天去環球影城排隊，「後面有幾個中國人很吵」，他正剛好與友人聊到「中國恢復帝制了」，「這群中國人聽到，全體突然沈默不語」。<br />\n網友紛紛留言：<br />\n好賤，不過我喜歡<br />\n記起來，遇到太吵的來用用看<br />\n學起來，嘻嘻，這樣支那人就會安靜聽了XDDDDD<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180228/1305853/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305853%2F&d=gv%2B9msUjp3Mb%2FfzWMe%2F9fk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3f4e97ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180228%2F1305853%2F&h=102715cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180228/1305853/</a>"},{"pid":"836a6faf6e692fd86acb9d7259b6fa10779fe503","tid":576472,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01441ea631c558cd658a95808ac98c653eb700c9","tid":576472,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"咒符"},{"pid":"9e581053a442a1b2013ef89e419605b6a0e604af","tid":576472,"uid":28433,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"證明台支一家 香港人講完班支那一樣嘈"},{"pid":"52900aaea788